641%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NYSE%20stock%20trader%20blowing%20a%20bubble%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691dc2e2abd5e944effb0318%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJOHANNES%20EISELE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarkets%20are%20split%20into%20two%20camps%20as%202025%20winds%20down%3A%20AI%20is%20a%20bubble%20or%20AI%20is%20not%20a%20bubble.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJohn%20Belton%20of%20Gabelli%20Funds%20notes%20that%20the%20market%20is%20prone%20to%20two%20distinct%20types%20of%20bubbles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20constant%20chatter%2C%20he%20doesn't%20think%20AI%20has%20formed%20into%20either%20type%20yet.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20either%20in%20one%20camp%20or%20the%20other%20as%202025%20comes%20to%20a%20close%3A%20you%20think%20AI%20is%20a%20bubble%20or%20that%20AI%20is%20not%20a%20bubble.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20those%20wondering%20where%20they%20stand%2C%20there's%20nuance%20in%20the%20debate%20to%20be%20aware%20of%2C%20specifically%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20bubble%20might%20AI%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20there%20are%20two%20kinds%2C%20according%20to%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20%2435%20billion%20Gabelli%20Funds.%20John%20Belton%20says%20stock%20market%20bubbles%20are%20either%20earnings-driven%20or%20valuation-driven.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20finance%20pros%2C%20he%20compared%20the%20current%20AI%20landscape%20to%20the%20dot-com%20era%2C%20noting%20that%20prices%20for%20top%20tech%20stocks%20today%20are%20high%20relative%20to%20profits%20but%20not%20overly%20so.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20he%20maintains%20that%20the%20AI%20market%20likely%20hasn't%20entered%20a%20valuation%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20argue%20we%20are%20in%20a%20valuation%20bubble%20currently.%20As%20an%20example%2C%20median%20'Mag%207'%20(seven%20largest%20tech%20co's)%20forward%20P%2FE%20was%20close%20to%2090x%20at%20YE99%20vs.%20~25x%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BValuations%20seem%20to%20simply%20reflect%20strong%20fundamentals%20without%20obvious%20excess.%20Are%20we%20in%20an%20earnings%20bubble%3F%20Time%20will%20tell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portfolio%20manager%20shared%20two%20reasons%20he%20doesn't%20think%20AI%20has%20fallen%20into%20an%20earnings%20bubble%20at%20present%2C%20though.%20The%20biggest%20reason%20is%20that%20while%20AI%20capex%20spending%20is%20high%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20it%20is%20being%20used%20to%20strengthen%20already-profitable%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20that%20the%20list%20of%20use%20cases%20for%20AI%20is%20growing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecond%20biggest%20reason%20to%20feel%20confident%20we%20are%20not%20in%20an%20earnings%20bubble%3A%20additional%20large-scale%20use%20cases%20are%20beginning%20to%20present%20themselves.%20Autonomous%20driving%2C%20robotics%2C%20life%20sciences%2C%20other%20scientific%20discovery%2C%20agentic%20software.%20We%20do%20need%20at%20least%20some%20of%20these%20use%20cases%20to%20become%20commercial%20%E2%80%94%20early%2C%20but%20there%20is%20promise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelton%20pointed%20to%20concerns%20surrounding%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Forcl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOracle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Favgo-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBroadcom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20both%20seen%20recent%20declines%20as%20investors%20question%20high%20capex%20spending%20and%20returns%20on%20AI%20investments.%20However%2C%20Belton%20added%20that%20he%20thinks%20both%20stocks%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20shake%20off%20the%20current%20volatility%2C%20and%20that%20Broadcom%20is%20among%20the%20top%20chip%20stocks%20to%20own%20right%20now.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portfolio%20manager%20is%20bullish%20on%20the%20AI%20trade's%20continued%20strength%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20but%20said%20investors%20are%20right%20to%20be%20cautious%20about%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-computing-deals-1-trillion-nvda-amd-orcl-crwv-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emassive%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20OpenAI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20any%20infrastructure%20cycle%20this%20too%20will%20be%20a%20cycle%20(question%20is%20not%20if%20we%20reach%20a%20peak%2C%20but%20when%20and%20how%20high%20the%20peak%20is)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-valuations-earnings-tech-magnificent-7-avgo-orcl-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765881001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69405fed832e0ef1ead63e70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-valuations-earnings-tech-magnificent-7-avgo-orcl-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Gabelli%20Funds%20says%20market%20bubbles%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20either%20valuations%20or%20earnings.%20AI%20isn't%20either%20kind%20of%20bubble%20just%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-valuations-earnings-tech-magnificent-7-avgo-orcl-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jerry%20Seinfeld%20Mourns%20Rob%20Reiner%2C%20Says%20%E2%80%98Seinfeld%E2%80%99%20Would%20%E2%80%98Have%20Never%20Happened%E2%80%99%20Without%20His%20Support%3A%20%E2%80%98He%20Saved%20Us%20From%20Cancellation%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765880909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F12%2FGettyImages