e%20middle%20market%20is%20headed%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20This%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20you%20feeling%20about%20the%20mid-cap%20M%26amp%3BA%20environment%20heading%20into%20next%20year%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20we're%20pretty%20optimistic%20on%202026.%20We%20have%20our%20highest%20backlog%20sell-sides%20that%20we've%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20private%20equity%20funds%20that%20need%20to%20return%20capital%20to%20their%20LPs.%20They%20need%20to%20sell%20assets.%20You%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20funds%20that%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20raise%20another%20fund%20but%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20portfolio%20companies%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20sell.%20You've%20got%20aging%20baby%20boomers%20and%20founder-owned%20businesses%20that%20children%20are%20not%20wanting%20to%20take%20over%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20does%20being%20local%20matter%20so%20much%20in%20your%20business%2C%20and%20how%20does%20that%20shape%20the%20way%20your%20team%20is%20built%20across%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dinner%2C%20bumping%20into%20a%20CEO%20on%20a%20Saturday%20on%20the%20soccer%20field%20or%20at%20kids'%20events.%20Like%20being%20in%20the%20communities%2C%20commercial%20banking%20is%20a%20local%20business.%20You've%20got%20to%20be%20in%20front%20of%20your%20clients.%20I%20once%20had%20a%20CEO%20tell%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20we%20like%20having%20you%20local%20is%20we%20like%20bumping%20into%20you%20and%20seeing%20you%20in%20the%20community.%20When%20you%20come%20and%20visit%20us%2C%20you're%20just%20paying%20a%20visit.%20You're%20not%20flying%20in%20from%20New%20York.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20chase%20fees%20or%20transactions%2C%20we%20chase%20relationships.%20Over%20time%2C%20if%20you%20do%20that%2C%20when%20that%20client%20decides%20that%20he%20has%20a%20transaction%20he%20needs%20you%20to%20work%20on%2C%20you've%20built%20that%20relationship%20over%20months%20and%20years.%20Local%20matters%20in%20our%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20allure%20of%20working%20outside%20of%20New%20York%2C%20and%20how%20can%20bankers%20who%20do%20stay%20plugged%20in%20with%20clients%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20think%20that%20analysts%20and%20associates%20should%20start%20out%20in%20New%20York%20to%20be%20in%20the%20center%20and%20the%20nexus%20of%20where%20it's%20happening.%20But%20then%20when%20you're%20tired%20of%20Manhattan%20or%20tired%20of%20commuting%20in%20from%20the%20tri-state%20area%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20places%20you%20can%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECome%20to%20New%20York%20or%20LA%2C%20the%20two%20big%20concentrations%20for%20us.%20Do%20your%20two%20years%20there%2C%20and%20then%20once%20you%20get%20promoted%20to%20associate%2C%20if%20you're%20from%20the%20Southeast%20or%20the%20Midwest%20or%20Texas%20or%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20we%20have%20these%20offices%20you%20can%20go%20work%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20us%20back%20to%20the%20beginning.%20How%20did%20JPMorgan's%20mid-cap%20banking%20group%20start%2C%20and%20why%20was%20it%20created%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20Barclays%20when%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20Doug%20Petno%2C%20now%20our%20CEO%20of%20JPMorgan's%20corporate%20investment%20bank.%20The%20firm%20asked%20me%20to%20move%20to%20Atlanta%20when%20we%20started%20this%20business%20about%2012%20years%20ago.%20Doug's%20first%20question%20was%3A%20What's%20our%20investment%20banking%20market%20share%3F%20And%20it%20was%20a%20low%20single%20digits%20compared%20to%20high%20single%20digits%20for%20the%20overall%20investment%20bank%20at%20JPMorgan.%20His%20first%20question%20was%2C%20'Why%20is%20that%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20originally%20from%20Tennessee%2C%20so%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20the%20southerner.%20Would%20you%20like%20to%20go%20to%20Atlanta%3F%26quot%3B%20We%20started%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Dallas%2C%20Chicago%2C%20and%20Atlanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20challenges%20did%20you%20face%20as%20you%20built%20the%20business%20from%20the%20ground%20up%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20needed%20to%20find%20the%20right%20mix%20of%20talent%20who%20were%20both%20highly%20skilled%20and%2C%20critically%2C%20excited%20to%20help%20build%20something%20new%20and%20enduring%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20isn't%20easy.%20Hiring%20is%20a%20full%20time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20looked%20for%20individuals%20who%20saw%20the%20opportunity%20to%20innovate%20and%20grow%2C%20and%20who%20were%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20with%20us.%20This%20endeavor%20was%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20very%20entrepreneurial.%20We%20are%20here%20building%20something%20brand%20new%20within%20JPMorgan%2C%20which%20is%20incredibly%20exciting%20but%20also%20incredibly%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20is%20AI%20changing%20the%20work%20your%20bankers%20do%20today%20and%20do%20you%20think%20it%20will%20change%20who%20gets%20into%20banking%20or%20affect%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20internal%20LLM%20that%20summarizes%20information%20and%20makes%20us%20smarter%20when%20we%20talk%20to%20clients.%20Tasks%20that%20used%20to%20take%20a%20day%20to%20do%2C%20you%20can%20now%20do%20in%20an%20hour%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20are%20not%20doing%20anywhere%20near%20as%20much%20as%20we%20should%20be.%20Drafting%20S-1s%2C%20drafting%20confidential%20information%20memoranda%2C%20drafting%20communications%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20that%20we%20should%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20efficiencies%20for%20the%20analysts'%20and%20associates'%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20cover%20more%20clients%2C%20which%20requires%20more%20people.%20Nobody%20likes%20staying%20up%20all%20night%20writing%20an%20S1.%20But%20if%20you%20can%20do%20an%20S1%20in%20six%20or%20seven%20hours%20by%20using%20AI%20and%20leave%20the%20office%20at%208%2C%20that's%20not%20eliminating%20people.%20It's%20just%20making%20it%20a%20better%20lifestyle%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20part%20of%20running%20this%20business%20keeps%20you%20up%20at%20night%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20focus%20is%20always%20on%20ensuring%20our%20team%20is%20set%20up%20for%20success%20and%20that%20we%20maintain%20our%20drive%20for%20excellence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20myriad%20macro%20factors%20causing%20uncertainty%20across%20the%20market%2C%20and%20we%20are%20of%20course%20monitoring%20them%20all%20closely.%20Our%20priority%20is%20to%20stay%20agile%20and%20proactive%20so%20we%20can%20continue%20delivering%20outstanding%20results%20for%20our%20clients%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20would%20you%20describe%20your%20leadership%20style%20and%20the%20culture%20you've%20built%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELead%20by%20example.%20There's%20nothing%20I%20would%20ask%20anybody%20on%20my%20team%20to%20do%20that%20I%20have%20not%20done%20or%20would%20not%20do%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20everyone%2C%20'This%20is%20just%20a%20job.%20Family%20comes%20first.%20Treat%20everyone%20you%20meet%20with%20respect.'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20trying%20to%20make%20this%20team%20the%20best%20it%20can%20be.%20Everyone%20from%20the%20top%20to%20the%20bottom%20matters.%20The%20MDs%20can't%20be%20successful%20without%20the%20analyst%2C%20and%20the%20analyst%20can't%20be%20successful%20without%20the%20MDs.%20Culture%20is%20not%20transferred%20over%20Zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20pretty%20easy.%20Just%20go%20give%20good%20advice%20to%20your%20clients.%20The%20rest%20of%20it%20will%20work%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-john-richert-middle-market-group-high-backl