m%2Funemployed-mom-burned-out-from-job-hunt-changing-approach-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20burned%20out%20from%202%20years%20of%20job%20hunting%2C%20so%20I%20changed%20everything%20about%20how%20I%20apply.%20I%20won't%20let%20the%20job%20market%20break%20my%20spirit%20anymore.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburnout-treatment-center-founder-ignored-symptoms-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20run%20a%20%24130%2C000-a-week%20burnout%20clinic%20for%20CEOs.%20After%20my%20life%20started%20to%20fall%20apart%2C%20I%20burned%20out%20too.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22559223bf-adf4-4194-828e-11209187a43c%5C%22%3EI%20fell%20into%20advertising%20and%20burned%20out%20quickly%20without%20realizing%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20I%20landed%20a%20job%20in%20advertising%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20that%20career%20path.%20As%20my%20career%20progressed%2C%20I%20would%20often%20stay%20at%20the%20office%20late%20into%20the%20night%20and%20miss%209%20p.m.%20dinner%20reservations.%20I%20felt%20creatively%20inspired%20by%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20but%20the%20hours%20were%20so%20long%20that%20I%20began%20to%20wonder%20what%20the%20point%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20whom%20I%20had%20met%20at%20work%20and%20just%20started%20dating%2C%20suggested%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-leave-google-job-no-regrets-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewe%20quit%20our%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20recover%20and%20travel%2C%20and%20I%20said%20yes.%20We%20were%20both%20experiencing%20burnout%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20even%20realize%20how%20bad%20it%20was%20until%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20several%20months%20saving%20money%20and%20planning%20before%20leaving%20our%20jobs%20in%20March%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c32dcae-842f-4a61-aeff-ad5e3398c82f%5C%22%3EWe%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20f