2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20were%20carried%20in%20stores%20and%20had%20enough%20orders%20coming%20in%2C%20we%20felt%20we%20couldn't%20keep%20up%20with%20both%20our%20corporate%20jobs%20and%20Bala.%20I%20left%20my%20advertising%20job%20first%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20followed%20a%20few%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20packing%20items%20at%20tables%20in%20a%20room%20with%20scattered%20boxes%20and%20a%20dog%20lying%20on%20the%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6939d48c71107c9f3457b7dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShipping%20out%20Bala%20orders.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Holloway%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20happened%2C%20and%20the%20fitness%20industry%20experienced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeloton-sales-surge-coronavirus-keeps-consumers-working-out-at-home-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20surge%20in%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20fitness%20industry%20experienced%20a%20decline%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20lay%20off%20our%20entire%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pregnant%20and%20felt%20like%20I%20didn't%20have%20enough%20stamina%20to%20take%20on%20the%20work%20of%2030%20people.%20It%20was%20a%20really%20demoralizing%20time%2C%20and%20the%20burnout%20hit%20me%20immediately%20because%20all%20of%20our%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20were%20on%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225f0a637-f641-4cf3-887c-2db4e02bb884%5C%22%3EThe%20second%20time%20I%20experienced%20burnout%2C%20I%20had%20to%20confront%20my%20mindset%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20let%20burnout%20destroy%20my%20health%20during%20my%20pregnancy.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20and%20learned%20the%20value%20of%20how%20I%20speak%20to%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20second%20experience%20with%20burnout%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyou-cant-mess-this-up-mantra-self-talk-weight-loss-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egiving%20myself%20a%20mantra%3C%2Fa%3E%20helps%20ground%20my%20anxiety.%20Sometimes%20it's%20something%20like%20'I'm%20calm%2C%20present%2C%20and%20have%20an%20abundance%20of%20time.'%20Repeating%20this%20helps%20when%20I'm%20feeling%20overwhelmed%20and%20burned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20control%20when%20stress%20creeps%20in%2C%20but%20I%20can%20control%20how%20I%20talk%20myself%20through%20it%20because%20my%20head%20is%20my%20reality%2C%20and%20I'm%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20positive%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20stands%20holding%20baby%20in%20Bala%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6939d01204d0f0a114f1c987%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatalie%20Holloway%20in%20the%20Bala%20store%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Holloway%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20rebuilding%20the%20business%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20that%20no%20matter%20how%20long%20it%20took%20for%20the%20company%20to%20recover%2C%20we%20were%20determined%20to%20see%20it%20through%20to%20the%20end.%20We%20had%20to%20prepare%20for%20a%20marathon%2C%20not%20a%20sprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20started%20regrowing%20our%20team%20back%20to%20its%20original%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2267df31bf-afb8-4c78-b053-5b15ad72446d%5C%22%3EThese%20small%20changes%20have%20made%20all%20the%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-in-yourself-hiring-life-coach-money-moves-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20with%20a%20life%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that's%20really%20helped.%20They're%20helping%20me%20understand%20what's%20on%20my%20to-do%20list%20that%20aligns%20with%20my%20values%2C%20which%20will%20give%20me%20energy%2C%20and%20what%20doesn't%20align%20with%20my%20values%2C%20which%20will%20deplete%20my%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we%20can't%20travel%20to%20cure%20burnout%20as%20we%20once%20did%2C%20I%20now%20take%20mini%20recovery%20trips%2C%20either%20for%20a%20weekend%2C%20a%20week%2C%20or%20a%20month%2C%20when%20I%20can.%20We%20sometimes%20visit%20Joshua%20Tree%20as%20a%20family%20to%20escape%20from%20LA%2C%20unwind%2C%20and%20mentally%20reset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20spend%20every%20July%20in%20Lakeside%2C%20Ohio.%20We%20don't%20make%20any%20plans.%20It's%20just%20our%20kids%20and%20us.%20We%20still%20do%20some%20work%2C%20but%20we're%20able%20to%20meaningfully%20downshift%20our%20lives%20in%20a%20way%20that%20recharges%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20have%20my%20mantras%20going%20now%2C%20and%20I've%20learned%20how%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20being%20kind%20to%20myself.%20I%20realized%20that%20burnout%20is%20inevitable%2C%20but%20it's%20about%20how%20I%20handle%20it.%20I%20try%20to%20prevent%20it%20by%20reminding%20myself%20that%20I'm%20working%20toward%20the%20long%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbala-bangles-founder-burnout-recovery-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765879501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6939d48c71107c9f3457b7dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbala-bangles-founder-burnout-recovery-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Burnout%20recovery%20inspired%20Bala%2C%20but%20founder%20Natalie%20Holloway%20found%20lasting%20relief%20through%20lifestyle%20changes%2C%20self-kindness%2C%20and%20using%20a%20life%20coach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aapplegate%40insider.com%20(Agnes%20Applegate)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22cano