0in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPentagon%20leaders%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-defense-contractors-future-drone-warfare-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshifted%20their%20focus%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20arguing%20that%20traditional%20defense%20contractors%20can't%20deliver%20new%20weapons%20fast%20or%20cheaply%20enough%20to%20meet%20today's%20fast-changing%20global%20threats.%20The%20Pentagon%20has%20pledged%20to%20pour%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20new%20technology%20and%20has%20issued%20requests%20for%20information%20on%20hybrid%2C%20autonomous%20air%20taxis%2C%20also%20known%20as%20vertical%20takeoff%20and%20landing%20vehicles%2C%20or%20VTOLs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlying-taxi%20makers%20including%20Archer%20Aviation%2C%20Joby%20Aviation%2C%20and%20Beta%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETechnologies%20say%20that%20gas-electric%20hybrid%20vehicles%20reminiscent%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Jetsons%26quot%3B%20could%20carry%20military%20cargo%20more%20cheaply%20and%20quietly%20than%20helicopters.%20Some%20of%20the%20designs%20under%20development%20for%20the%20battlefield%20incorporate%20autonomous%20technology%20that%20could%20detect%20and%20avoid%20threats.%20The%20aircraft%20could%20be%20used%20for%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%2C%20or%20moving%20supplies%20and%20equipment%2C%20these%20companies%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20air-taxi%20makers%20are%20racing%20to%20develop%20cutting-edge%20technology%20as%20Chinese%20companies%20like%20EHang%20do%20the%20same.%20The%20VTOL%20industry%20is%20still%20young%2C%20and%20China%20hasn't%20yet%20cornered%20the%20air-taxi%20market%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-startup-firestorm-mobile-drone-factories-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20it%20has%20for%20smaller%2C%20aerial%20combat%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20can%20fundamentally%20go%20further%20and%20faster%20than%20a%20helicopter%2C%20then%20we%20have%20a%20tool%20that's%20more%20powerful%20than%20what%20the%20Chinese%20are%20going%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Beta's%20CEO%2C%20Kyle%20Clark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommercial%20air-taxi%20designs%20are%20typically%20electric.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESwapping%20the%20electric%20battery%20for%20a%20hybrid%20engine%20will%20help%20the%20aircraft%20carry%20more%20weight%20and%20travel%20farther%2C%20a%20key%20consideration%20for%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20executives%20from%20Joby%20and%20Beta%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beta's%20dual-use%20aircraft%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69409a2004eda4732f2d918d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223520%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeta's%20dual-use%20aircraft%3Cp%3EBeta%20Technologies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EArcher%2C%20Joby%2C%20and%20Beta%20are%20all%20developing%20military%20VTOLs%20that%20can%20fly%20autonomously.%20In%20Beta's%20battlefield%20version%2C%20a%20human%20must%20plug%20in%20destination%20coordinates%20for%20the%20aircraft%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20can%20help%20it%20navigate%20to%20the%20destination%2C%20said%20Clark.%20Configuring%20the%20aircraft%20to%20operate%20without%20a%20pilot%20makes%20it%20lighter%20than%20a%20commercial%20air%20taxi%2C%20since%20it%20doesn't%20require%20seats%20or%20the%20safety%20and%20avionics%20systems%20that%20are%20necessary%20when%20transporting%20people%2C%20Clark%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClinching%20coveted%20contracts%20from%20the%20Pentagon%20would%20add%20air-taxi%20manufacturers%20to%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20dual-use%20companies%20that%20sell%20to%20commercial%20clients%20as%20well%20as%20to%20the%20government.%20Joby%20is%20collaborating%20with%20traditional%20defense%20firm%20L3Harris%20on%20a%20military%20VTOL%20and%20test-flew%20a%20prototype%20in%20November.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArcher%20is%20developing%20one%20with%20Anduril%20Industries%20for%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20Archer's%20CEO%2C%20Adam%20Goldstein.%20Anduril%20is%20also%20developing%20a%20military%20VTOL%20called%20Omen%20in%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Emirati%20defense%20giant%20Edge%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e98e2e8d-60e8-457f-9113-209a9d09e709%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPermission%20to%20fly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20air-taxi%20makers'%20biggest%20hurdles%20to%20commercial%20adoption%20is%20securing%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20certification%2C%20though%20the%20Trump%20administration%20is%20attempting%20to%20make%20it%20easier.%20In%20September%2C%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Sean%20Duffy%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Ftrumps-transportation-secretary-sean-p-duffy-unveils-new-plan-fast-track-advanced-air%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWASHINGTON%252C%2520D.C.%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520U.S.%2520Transportation%2520Secretary%2Cmanufacturing%2520jobs%2520and%2520economic%2520opportunity.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20FAA%20program%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20permits%20VTOL%20companies%20to%20test-fly%20piloted%20and%20unmanned%20aircraft%20before%20receiving%20federal%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoby%20is%20leading%20the%20pack%20in%20the%20certification%20race%2C%20having%20cleared%20four%20of%20the%20five%20stages%20for%20commercial%20clearance.%20Archer%20and%20Joby%20hope%20to%20fly%20commercially%20as%20early%20as%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20defense%20adoption%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20companies%20would%20need%20the%20Defense%20Department%20to%20deem%20their%20VTOLs%20ready%20to%20fly%2C%20Goldstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETaylor%20Rains%20contributed%20to%20this%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-co