0McCarthy%2FSportsfile%20for%20Collision%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShiloh%20Luckey%20founded%20a%20tax-compliance%20startup%20and%20has%20a%20popular%20TikTok%20channel%20where%20she%20gives%20financial%20advice.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20raised%20a%20%245.5%20million%20seed%20round%20led%20by%20Craft%20Ventures%2C%20the%20VC%20cofounded%20by%20investor%20and%20White%20House%20advisor%20David%20Sacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELuckey%20is%20under%20federal%20criminal%20investigation%20for%20alleged%20fraud%20and%20is%20also%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShiloh%20Luckey%2C%20founder%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20ComplYant%2C%20a%20Los-Angeles-based%20tax-compliance%20startup%20that%20raised%20more%20than%20%2413%20million%20from%20top%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20is%20under%20federal%20criminal%20investigation%20for%20alleged%20securities%20and%20bank%20fraud%2C%20according%20to%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20civil%20complaint%2C%20the%20SEC%20has%20charged%20Luckey%20with%20violating%20securities%20laws%20for%20using%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20company%20funds%20to%20pay%20for%20her%20home%2C%20Super%20Bowl%20tickets%2C%20and%20a%20destination%20wedding%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%20The%20SEC%20alleges%20she%20painted%20a%20rosy%20picture%20of%20the%20company's%20booming%20revenue%20when%20ComplYant%20never%20brought%20in%20more%20than%20%24620%20in%20monthly%20revenue%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Ffiles%2Flitigation%2Fcomplaints%2F2025%2Fcomp26424.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReached%20by%20telephone%2C%20Luckey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20anything%20to%20offer%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20hung%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20face%20far%20less%20regulatory%20scrutiny%20than%20public%20companies%2C%20and%20founders%20sometimes%20present%20overly%20optimistic%20growth%20stories%20while%20VCs%20rush%20to